eally deleted, or at least to receive another message when this has been done.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Currently, <code>entity_delete</code> request messages are pushed onto a queue by <code>World</code> to be handled later. However, the response to the message is sent immediately, when the entity has not yet been really deleted. I would expect the response to an <code>entity_delete</code> to be sent only when the entity is really deleted, or at least to receive another message when this has been done.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "6.0", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/170782.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2015-09-14T12:41:30.998773+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-05-10T00:14:56.774104+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1738}